name: Wild Thongs, Bourke Lane
description:
Red rubber thongs, pair
Sydney, Australia
4 January 2011

The meme of the abandoned shoe had not yet revealed itself. It was just a funny moment. “Thong itself is such a funny word” thought Jeffrey. He was such a slave to fashion, yet dressed abominably. 

-----

The Lost Shoe Project brings together participants from around the world, in a performance piece documented in close-to-real-time as a sequence of photographic images of lost or abandoned shoes. The Collector presents this first array of his most loved images.
